{{Top|leg}}
'''Stimcaf''' was a beverage served warm, presumably containing large amounts of caffeine. Like [[stim tea]] it was often consumed to raise alertness and to keep from falling asleep.

==Behind the scenes==
[[Caf/Legends|Caf]], stimcaf, [[coffeine]] and [[coffee]] are almost certainly meant to be variations of [[Wikipedia:Coffee|coffee]] or caffeine.

